      "instruction": "<p><strong>Prepare the vegetables and stock </strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>brown</strong>&nbsp;<strong>onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (skins on). Peel and slice (don't chop!) the <strong>garlic</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Strip the <strong>rosemary leaves</strong>&nbsp;from the stems and chop finely. Discard the stems.</p>\r\n<p>Dissolve the <strong>beef stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;and<strong> Just Add Wine sachet<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span><strong> boiled&nbsp;water</strong>.</p>",
