    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add the duck legs and pop in the oven</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sit the <strong>browned duck legs</strong>, skin side&nbsp;up, over the<strong>&nbsp;sauce </strong>and cover with the lid.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Put the dish in the oven&nbsp;for an initial 1 hour 20 minutes or until the <strong>duck</strong> is tender and cooked through, and the sauce is thick and rich.</p>\r\n<p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
