      "instruction": "<p><strong>Prepare the cavolo&nbsp;nero and garnishes</strong></p>\r\n<p>After 1 hour, chop the <strong>cavolo nero</strong> roughly, including the stalks.</p>\r\n<p>Grate the <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>pine nuts</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 5-6 minutes or until golden. Once golden, remove from the oven and set aside until serving.</p>\r\n<p>Re-boil a kettle.</p>",
