    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add cheese and seasoning to the polenta </strong></p>\r\n<p>Once thickened, add the <strong>grated cheese</strong>&nbsp;with a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> and whisk to combine. Taste the <strong>polenta</strong> and&nbsp;add another pinch of&nbsp;<strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>&nbsp;if needed. This is your <strong>cheese polenta</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Re-boil a kettle.</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped cavolo nero</strong> to a colander over the sink and pour over all of the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>boiled water</strong></span> until bright green and wilted.</p>",
